Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/purgatory: remove PGO flags

References: bsc#1194869
Patch-mainline: v6.4 or v6.4-rc7 (next release)
Git-commit: 20188baceb7a1463dc0bcb0c8678b69c2f447df6

If profile-guided optimization is enabled, the purgatory ends up with
multiple .text sections.  This is not supported by kexec and crashes the
system.

Link: https://lkml.kernel.org/r/20230321-kexec_clang16-v7-3-b05c520b7296@chromium.org
Fixes: 930457057abe ("kernel/kexec_file.c: split up __kexec_load_puragory")
